cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with dense visual SLAM and learning depth from images. 
2. cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of the proposed representation in a monocular dense SLAM system. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper uses auto-encoders and optimisation techniques to learn the compact representation. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with learning a representation for probabilistic inference. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) is also a possible category as the paper deals with representing scene geometry in real-time 3D perception systems.
